        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", from anything like a false accusation. Neither bring one, nor countenance one, else those mayest cause the death of an innocent and righteous man, and bring down on thyself the vengeance of him, who ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
